Class OAPopup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.web.OAHtmlElement
      • com.viaoa.web.OAPopup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OAJspComponent, OAJspRequirementsInterface, Serializable

    public class OAPopup
extends OAHtmlElement
    turn an html element into a popup. if location is on viewport edge, then it will use the slide affect, else fade.
    Author:
    vvia
